毒出嚟<br />\n初頭打佢地嘅血都偏高 未必打得爆<br />\n<br />\n攻略篇可以再加<br />\n- 善用無敵Gear 如果效力未完 <br />\n可以的話 用盡晒8秒先攞第二件<br />\n- 保命重要過殺毒 分數唔會攞少咗 但三條命用晒就會死 但都唔可以積累太多BOSS"},{"pid":"b136814bd48e59cb08ba606a852e37f842e27824","tid":1953740,"uid":169944,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T13:10:35.000Z","msg":"召喚奔走15厘米巴打，我同你攞左#2<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cbb00a525b5e13095c0ec8402bf57b26a35f63f","tid":1953740,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T15:12:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/nYL6uaP.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FnYL6uaP.gif&h=c164da23&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5c2a61be2ebefdbfc050b325ddbc096914642077","tid":1953740,"uid":30836,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T15:58:58.000Z","msg":"口罩係只限一個先啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n攻略可以再加：<br />\n- 雙打如果同時間拎道具 可以兩邊都用到 要有默契或同時等佢跌落地。"},{"pid":"1656659926d511e8040734999aa4fc4d847ea1b2","tid":1953740,"uid":55438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T16:05:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ea3f192aaf21fc6a72db3bb02c1e566983f03e6d","tid":1953740,"uid":135281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T16:24:35.000Z","msg":"拿左無敵可以不停博身肉博同BOSS打<br />\n因為近身隻boss 都扣血扣得好快<br />\n手腳快一般8秒可以秒2隻小王"},{"pid":"1add44f92beb592d4c0ef16bc15fbd64409caea8","tid":1953740,"uid":34213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T16:24:40.000Z","msg":"三萬分<br />\n後期唔郁好過郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跳起我估快啲打中boss會快啲死咁解"},{"pid":"e0e2e673d017be3a7af5c0c7324b3fb94ff94fd8","tid":1953740,"uid":66546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T16:32:35.000Z","msg":"三萬 thx<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},